Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity

Class TaskEntity

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity.TaskEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class TaskEntity extends Object implements Serializable
The TaskEntity class represents the "task" table in the database. Each instance of this class corresponds to a single row in the table.
